a result of or contributed to by the negligence of Green Rabbit Holdings.</p><p>Green Rabbit Holdings reserves the right, but has no obligation, to license updated iterations of GREEN RABBIT GAME separately and under different terms.</p><p>11. Use of Data</p><p>11.1 Use of Data by Green Rabbit Holdings</p><p>You agree that Green Rabbit Holdings may collect and use technical data and related information - including but not limited to technical information about your devices, systems and application software, and peripherals - that is gathered periodically to facilitate the provision of updates, support, and other services to you (if any) related to GREEN RABBIT GAME. Green Rabbit Holdings may use this information in a form which does not identify individuals.</p><p>Green Rabbit Holdings will use industry standard administrative, physical and technical safeguards to protect any data collected in accordance with this provision and the Privacy Policy. If a court or government agency orders us to disclose any of your personal data, you will be promptly notified so that an appropriate protective order or other remedy can be obtained unless the court or government agency prohibits prior notification.</p><p>11.2 Publicity of Data</p><p>You acknowledge and agree that certain data pertaining to you, which you may view as sensitive, will be accessible to the public through the WAX Blockchain. Such data includes, but is not limited to, information identifying and/or otherwise pertaining to your User Account and your WAX account.</p><p>11.3 Privacy Policy</p><p>Unless specified otherwise herein, all use of data shall be subject to Green Rabbit Holdings privacy policy, as amended from time to time (the "Privacy Policy"). The Privacy Policy, as currently in force, is available on the GREEN RABBIT GAME website.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>12. Loss of Data</p><p>In the event that any information or data (including without limitation in respect of in-game characters, achievements, Virtual Items or general GREEN RABBIT GAME gameplay) relating to you or your use of any of GREEN RABBIT GAME, the Website, Materials and Services held by Green Rabbit Holdings or any third-party on behalf of or in coordination with Green Rabbit Holdings is lost, corrupted or otherwise no longer reasonably available or accessible as determined by Green Rabbit Holdings in its sole discretion, you agree that to the greatest extent permissible at law Green Rabbit Holdings will have no liability to you of any nature relating to any such information or data.</p><p>13. No Representations and Warranties</p><p>Green Rabbit Holdings does not make any representation or give any warranty in respect to any characteristics of GREEN RABBIT GAME. All warranties are expressly excluded to the maximal extent permitted under applicable laws. In particular, while Green Rabbit Holdings has endeavoured to take all reasonable measures and apply appropriate care in the preparation of the content of GREEN RABBIT GAME, the Website, Materials and Services, we do neither represent nor warrant that:</p><p>- GREEN RABBIT GAME runs uninterrupted and error-free;</p><p>- the use of GREEN RABBIT GAME is fit for any particular purpose and does not infringe upon any third party's intellectual property rights;</p><p>- any information contained in GREEN RABBIT GAME and/or any of the Website, Materials or Services is accurate, adequate, complete or error free or that any Posts or Images are compliant with the Posting Policy and Image Policy.</p><p>You use GREEN RABBIT GAME at your sole risk. GREEN RABBIT GAME is provided to you on an "as is"-basis, with all faults and without express or implied warranty of any kind.</p><p>Green Rabbit Holdings is not an investment advisor and GREEN RABBIT GAME is not a financial platform or vehicle. Green Rabbit holdings does not provide any financial advice, offers of profit nor return on investment (ROI). GREEN RABBIT GAME is strictly a Wax Blockchain based multi-activity interactive game.</p><p>14. Liability</p><p>To the maximum extent allowed by law, Green Rabbit Holdings liability towards you and your associates (whether contractual or otherwise) with respect to this Agreement and the use of GREEN RABBIT GAME shall be limited to damages resulting from wilful misconduct by Green Rabbit Holdings.</p><p>15. Indemnity</p><p>You herewith undertake, irrespective of any fault and knowledge, to fully compensate and indemnify Green Rabbit Holdings and/or any of its corporate bodies, affiliates and related parties (as directed by Green Rabbit Holdings) against any and all damage incurred or sustained in contract, tort, equity, statute, regulation or otherwise by Green Rabbit Holdings and/or any of its corporate bodies, affiliates and related parties, including without limitation any economic loss, loss of turnover, profits, business or goodwill, whether direct or consequential, in connection with (i) your actions within GREEN RABBIT GAME, and/or (ii) your breach of these Terms of Use and/or (ii) your or any third party's use of video content created or distributed by you under the permitted streaming and video sharing provisions pursuant to Section 13.</p><p>You acknowledge and agree that, in the event of a third party claim in the event that you breach these Terms of Use or in connection with your or any third party's use of video content created or distributed by you under the permitted streaming and video sharing provisions pursuant to Section 13, in particular in the event of a claim whereas any of your actions, Posts or Images in connection with GREEN RABBIT GAME infringe on any third party's intellectual property rights, you (and not Green Rabbit Holdings) will be responsible to bear the cost of the investigation, defense, settlement and discharge of any such claim. You will, however, promptly notify Green Rabbit Holdings in writing of such a claim and Green Rabbit Holdings shall have the right, within its sole discretion, to direct any procedural actions in which it has a direct or indirect interest.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>16. External Links</p><p>Links to external websites are provided as a convenience and for informational purposes only; they do not constitute an endorsement or an approval by Green Rabbit Holdings of any of the products, services or opinions of the relevant entity or organization or individual. Green Rabbit Holdings bears no responsibility for the accuracy, legality or content of external sites or for that of subsequent links. Green Rabbit Holdings recommends that you read the privacy policies and the terms of use of external websites before you make use thereof or provide personal information on any external websites.</p><p>17. No Partnership or Agency</p><p>Nothing in this Agreement, shall be construed to establish, and the Parties shall refrain from any representation or other act that could lead any affiliate or third party to believe that they have established any form of partnership or company, and/or an agency.</p><p>18. Breach and Remedies</p><p>You understand and agree that observance of your obligations hereunder is of significant importance to Green Rabbit Holdings and that, if you breach this Agreement, Green Rabbit Holdings would incur serious losses and other detrimental consequences which might not easily be cured.</p><p>If you breach any provision of or undertaking under this Agreement, Green Rabbit Holdings shall have the right to seek specific performance in respect of your obligations under this Agreement, including but not limited to the right to request that you cease and/or desist from committing any breach of such obligations, whether or not this forces you to abandon any commercial activity or not to pursue any opportunities at that time (cease and desist injunction).</p><p>Green Rabbit Holdings has the right to seek interim legal protection to prevent detrimental consequences and effects that cannot easily be remedied or to ensure an effective enforcement of your