ddress (the "Notification Address"). You acknowledge and accept that Green Rabbit Holdings shall send any notifications to you hereunder (also including any invoice), by way of simple unencrypted email to the Notification Address. Any such notification shall be deemed received when it is sent by Green Rabbit Holdings to the Notification Address.</p><p>You undertake to keep the Notification Address valid and in effect for the entire duration of this Agreement or to promptly notify Green Rabbit Holdings in writing prior to any change of the Notification Address.</p><p>Notices to Green Rabbit Holdings shall be made by registered mail to Green Rabbit Holdings registered address.</p><p>20.2 Amendments</p><p>Green Rabbit Holdings reserves the right to amend this Agreement from time to time upon placing any such amendments on the Website or by providing you direct notice of any such changes. Your continued use of any of the Website, Materials and Services thereafter will be deemed to as acceptance by you of any such changes to this Agreement.</p><p>20.3 Assignment</p><p>You may not assign any of your rights or obligations hereunder, whether by operation of the law or otherwise. Green Rabbit Holdings may assign this Agreement without your consent and in its sole and absolute discretion. </p><p>20.4 No Waiver</p><p>The failure of Green Rabbit Holdings to exercise or enforce any right under this Agreement shall neither be deemed to be a waiver of that right nor operate to bar the exercise or enforcement of it at any time or times thereafter.</p><p>20.5 Severability</p><p>If any provision, or portion of a provision, contained in the Agreement is invalid or unenforceable, the remaining provisions, or the remaining portion of such provision, shall remain in full force and effect. Instead of the invalid provision, a rule shall apply that achieves as closely as possible the intention of the parties in drafting the invalid provision.</p><p>20.6 Applicable Law and Jurisdiction</p><p